Customize GT table

Source: R/gt_custom_themes.R
gt_theme_ms.Rd

Customize Table Theme with the gt Package.

Usage

gt_theme_ms(data = automaton::penguins)

Arguments

gt_tbl

Input GT table not just data frame. First convert data frame/tibble to GT table then input that gt table to the function

Value

Returns the gt table using the customized theme

Examples

library(automaton)
library(gt)
tbl <- automaton::penguins
gt_tbl <- tbl |>
            dplyr::count(species) |>
            gt::gt()

gt_tbl |> gt_theme_ms()
